title: CASTILLO - The Incredible Shrinking Duke [Vol.2] (2006)
description:
CASTILLO - The Incredible Shrinking Duke [Vol.2] (2006)

Enter the whimsical world of Castillo, an imaginative young dragon, in this clay animation children's series that will charm the whole family with its witty attitude. Determined to improve his medieval village, the engaging Castillo is always introducing new inventions -- including air conditioning, printing and a flying machine. The helpful fire-breather also tries to keep the villagers up-to-date by sharing any new information he discovers.Contains episodes:

1.The Incredible Shrinking Duke
2.Music is the Food of Love
3.Oil Makes the World Go Round
4.Fly Me to the Moon
